      • readDimacs

        private Graph readDimacs()
        This method is used to read Graphs that are in the DIMACS format. More info about the DIMACS format can be found a http://prolland.free.fr/works/research/dsat/dimacs.html
        Returns:
        a Graph if it conforms to the DIMACS format, null otherwise

      • getFormat

        private GraphReader.Format getFormat(String file_name)
        This method identifies the format of the file by its extension. Each graph file has a different format.
        Returns:
        The format type in which the graph is stored.
